<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期一早上，在学校，凯蒂很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，她也很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果她不和卢克、卡洛斯和好，她的方块舞计划就完了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她递给乔伊一张纸条，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帮我把这个传给卡洛斯。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她递给奥利维亚一张纸条，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帮我把这个传给卢克。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两张纸条写着同样的话：“今天晚上过来练舞！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“B-ù 是 ‘不’！” 卡洛斯写道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可能。” 卢克写道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“该劳拉发表了，主题是关于眼睛的。” 贝柔老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉拿着一个粉色的手提箱走到教室前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家好。我很担心大家的眼睛！” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们一定要保护眼睛！” 她的眼睛睁得很大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“像剪刀这样锋利的东西一定要小心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊想起了曾经凯蒂拿着剪刀从楼上跑下来的情景。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她踢了一下凯蒂的书桌，让她好好儿听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉继续说：“像飞镖这样的东西也一定要小心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有像爆竹这样的物品，油漆清除剂这种液体也要小心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉把手放进了她的手提箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是安全镜。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它可以戴在普通眼镜上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当你做科学实验或使用工具时，请戴上它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉拿出更多的眼镜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是很酷的运动眼镜，我打垒球时会戴它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有太阳镜，保护眼睛不受阳光的伤害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你看不清书本或黑板，请告诉你的父母。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可能需要一副眼镜了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一直戴着眼镜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我摘下眼镜，看着就会很奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们看！我看着像另一个人似的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉关上她的手提箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 说完，她回到了她的座位上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真不错！” 乔伊对她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一个是乔伊发表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要介绍一下怎么建立友谊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，在我发表时，希望大家能做一个友好的听众。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请把身体转向我，看着我的眼睛。” 乔伊看了看大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。现在，请大家集中精力听我发表！” 她笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家准备好了吗？” 大家都向乔伊点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果一个人看起来很亲切，请说一些友好的话，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就是建立新友谊的办法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可以主动帮忙拿东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>或者，你也可以让他帮助你！” 凯蒂点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想起了在图书馆里奥利维亚向她寻求帮助的场景。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转头向她的新朋友微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也可以夸一个人头发好看或运动鞋很可爱。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在开学第一天，劳拉告诉奥利维亚她的夏威夷果项链很酷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就是一句很友好的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊深吸了一口气，向劳拉笑了笑，继续说着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有很多方法可以交到好朋友。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要友好，不要取笑你的朋友。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说的是‘不要捉弄朋友’的意思吗？” 凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看卢克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要成为一个言而有信的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要违背诺言或计划。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克和卡洛斯看着凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要太霸道。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么大家都看着我？” 凯蒂大声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做个好听众。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是说，不要打断别人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，这个很重要。” 乔伊继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你跟朋友们吵架了，要尽快和好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说 ‘对不起，我不该那么说。’ ，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>或者说 ‘我错了！’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊把手伸进了一个纸袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是友谊测定仪。” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，这个教室里有些朋友的行为让这个友谊测定仪指向了哭脸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看着卢克、卡洛斯和凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些朋友吵架了。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我觉得该和好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>